biocode.fims.run

Class Process

  • java.lang.Object
    • biocode.fims.run.Process

  • public class Process
extends java.lang.Object
    Core class for running fims processes. Here you specify the input file, configuration file, output folder, and a expedition code, which is used to specify Bcid roots in the BCID (http://code.google.com/p/bcid/) system. The main class is configured to run this from the command-line while the class itself can be extended to run in different situations, while specifying fimsPrinter and FimsInputter classes for a variety of styles of output and input
